hether to increment the version numbers, requiring users to agree to the new terms and conditions before they can use the company portal."},{"content":"<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>A number of Intune policies have been renamed<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> to make them more consistent across the product and easier for you to find.","pos":[26276,26401],"source":"**A number of Intune policies have been renamed** to make them more consistent across the product and easier for you to find."},{"content":"For a list of all available Intune policies, see <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>Use policies to manage computers and mobile devices with Microsoft Intune<ept id=\"p1\">](https://technet.microsoft.com/library/dn743712.aspx)</ept>.","pos":[26402,26580],"source":" For a list of all available Intune policies, see [Use policies to manage computers and mobile devices with Microsoft Intune](https://technet.microsoft.com/library/dn743712.aspx)."},{"content":"<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>PKCS #12 (.PFX) Certificate Profiles<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> are available for Android 4.0 or later, and Windows 10 (desktop and mobile) and later.","pos":[26583,26710],"source":"**PKCS #12 (.PFX) Certificate Profiles** are available for Android 4.0 or later, and Windows 10 (desktop and mobile) and later."},{"content":"Using .PFX does not require an NDES server.","pos":[26711,26754]},{"content":"Learn how to use .PFX certificate profiles in <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>Enable access to company resources using certificate profiles with Microsoft Intune<ept id=\"p1\">](http://technet.microsoft.com/library/dn818904.aspx)</ept>","pos":[26755,26938],"source":" Learn how to use .PFX certificate profiles in [Enable access to company resources using certificate profiles with Microsoft Intune](http://technet.microsoft.com/library/dn818904.aspx)"},{"pos":[26941,27183],"content":"<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Corporate Boundaries settings for Windows 10 Desktop and Mobile<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> enable granular VPN settings, as described in <bpt id=\"